// --- src/component/Page/Admin/AdminDashboardPage.js ---
// REVISED: Acts as a navigation hub

import React from 'react';
// Import MUI components
import {
    Container, Typography, Box, Button, Paper, Grid, Card, CardContent, CardActions
} from '@mui/material';
// Import MUI Icons
import PeopleAltIcon from '@mui/icons-material/PeopleAlt'; // For Customers
import WorkOutlineIcon from '@mui/icons-material/WorkOutline'; // For Applications
import ManageAccountsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ManageAccounts'; // For Employee Actions
// Import React Router Link
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';

export default function AdminDashboardPage() {
    // This page is now just for navigation. Logic for customer approvals is moved.

    return (
        <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 4, mb: 4 }}>
            {/* Dashboard Header */}
            <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: { xs: 2, md: 3 }, mb: 4, textAlign: 'center' }}>
                <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
                    Admin Dashboard
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                    Select an area to manage customer accounts, job applications, or perform employee actions.
                </Typography>
            </Paper>

            {/* Action Cards Grid */}
            <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center" alignItems="stretch">

                {/* Card 1: Customer Approvals */}
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                    <Card sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', '&:hover': { boxShadow: 6 }, transition: 'box-shadow 0.3s' }}>
                        <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                            <PeopleAltIcon color="primary" sx={{ fontSize: 60, mb: 2 }} />
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                                Customer Approvals
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ minHeight: '40px' }}>
                                View and manage pending customer registrations.
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                        <CardActions sx={{ justifyContent: 'center', pb: 3 }}>
                            <Button
                                component={RouterLink}
                                // *** Ensure path matches App.js ***
                                to="/admin/pending-customers"
                                size="medium"
                                variant="contained"
                                color="primary"
                            >
                                Manage Customers
                            </Button>
                        </CardActions>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>

                {/* Card 2: Job Applications */}
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                    <Card sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', '&:hover': { boxShadow: 6 }, transition: 'box-shadow 0.3s' }}>
                        <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                            <WorkOutlineIcon color="secondary" sx={{ fontSize: 60, mb: 2 }} />
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                                Job Applications
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ minHeight: '40px' }}>
                                Review submitted job applications and manage the hiring process.
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                        <CardActions sx={{ justifyContent: 'center', pb: 3 }}>
                            <Button
                                component={RouterLink}
                                // *** Ensure path matches App.js ***
                                to="/admin/applications"
                                size="medium"
                                variant="contained"
                                color="secondary"
                            >
                                Manage Applications
                            </Button>
                        </CardActions>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>

                {/* Card 3: Employee Actions Portal (Link for Admin) */}
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                     <Card sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', '&:hover': { boxShadow: 6 }, transition: 'box-shadow 0.3s' }}>
                        <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                             <ManageAccountsIcon sx={{ fontSize: 60, mb: 2, color: 'success.main' }} />
                             <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2">
                                Employee Actions
                             </Typography>
                             <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ minHeight: '40px' }}>
                                Access employee functions like deposit, withdrawal, etc.
                             </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                        <CardActions sx={{ justifyContent: 'center', pb: 3 }}>
                            <Button
                                component={RouterLink}
                                // *** Ensure path matches App.js ***
                                to="/employee/dashboard"
                                size="medium"
                                variant="contained"
                                color="success"
                            >
                                Go to Employee Portal
                            </Button>
                        </CardActions>
                    </Card>
                </Grid>

            </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
}
